Facebook to remove comments that insult migrants and refugees
Facebook is removing posts and comments that negatively assess migrants and refugees.
In addition, the social network will provide financial support to organizations that collect user complaints about illegal content.
Facebook is working with the German Ministry of Justice to combat xenophobia and racism online.
